Patch Set 3:

Hi Mark,

I lifted all info upwards on this change that had not dropped to debug and involved error messages. As stated on the OS logging standards INFO level messages should not contain  anything error related. I think/hope I did not lift anything that would not benefit operators on normal production.

I know it is thin line, but the previous situation where ops are complaining that they have to run on debugging because otherwise they will not get what they need from the logs is not sustainable either. 

Anyone,
Please feel free to flag any specifics. I'm more than happy to discuss about these.
